@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_degubt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.95 - wp.sin((v0 + 0.12 / tmp + 0.64)))
    v1 = v1
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(0.17))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.16 + v2 + 0.27)) * (v1 * (v2 + 0.66 * v0 + 0.40)))
    tmp = 0.40
    data[tid] = v0
